data.description: Start Fresh - Buy New! Why buy someone else's used home when you can BUY NEW. The most energy efficient home you can buy is a new home. SOLAR INCLUDED - YOU OWN THE SOLAR!!! NO SOLAR LEASE to worry about. This well priced 4 bedroom 2 full bath home, located in a desirable neighborhood, comes with 1948 square feet of living space, an over-sized 576 sq ft finished garage (with Wi-Fi door opener) and the roof is concrete tile. It has a great room with eating area and ceiling fans along with an indoor laundry room. The kitchen has a HUGE walk-in pantry, quartz counters with soft close cabinets and plenty of counter / cabinet space for all your cooking needs. The bedrooms have ceiling fans and mirrored wardrobe doors (except master bedroom which will have a nice walk-in closet). Outside you will find a covered front porch, a nice size back patio for you to relax on and RV parking on the side. All that it needs is your personal touches to make this your home! Home is connected to sewer. (Builder  reserves the right to make changes from pics)
